Step 1: Start
Step 2: Store Input Values and Output Address in Required Registers
Step 3: Clear Carry
Step 4: Move First Operand into Accumulator
Step 5: Subtract Second Operand from Accumulator
Step 6: Store Value in Accumulator into Output Register
Step 7: Increment Output Pointer
Step 8: If there is no carry, go to Step 11
Step 9: Move Carry into AL
Step 10: Move AL into Output Address
Step 11: Stop